&lt;p&gt;Band 2 - Ward Clerk, De La Mare/Beckett&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Part time 15 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a ward administrator to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be for a Wednesday and Friday on a busy Surgical/ orthopaedic unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be the first contact for patients attending the ward. the candidate should be computer literate and have good organizational skills, with a friendly telephone manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jane Simpson 01727 897459&lt;/p&gt;
